[09/01/2018 00:21:25] <font color="#ffff00">La Ley contra la Propaganda</font>
[09/01/2018 00:21:25] <font color="#ffff00">Homosexual</font>
[09/01/2018 00:21:28] <font color="#ffff00">ha envalentonado a los radicales</font>
