[09/01/2018 00:26:02] <font color="#ffff00">o las fake news,</font>
[09/01/2018 00:26:06] <font color="#ffff00">las noticias falsas.</font>
[09/01/2018 00:26:09] <font color="#ffff00">Pero hoy su influencia</font>
