[09/01/2018 23:45:26] <font color="#ffff00">Nos saltaremos el mandamiento</font>
[09/01/2018 23:45:26] <font color="#ffff00">canadiense que dice:</font>
[09/01/2018 23:45:29] <font color="#ffff00">No te intentarás colar .</font>
